title: The Gals Are Back Together!
itunes:title: The Gals Are Back Together!
description:
After over 2 months, Brooke and Danielle are back together on the podcast!  The two discuss what they have been up to recently as well as clearing the air on some of the rumors circulating the internet about what’s REALLY been going on.  The gals also discuss the concept of birthday posts, opinions on snapchat, social media addiction and Brooke shares some recent revelations from her dating life!

Check out the Business of The Week, Sier.ra! http://sierrabrayy.com/
